1. The Autonomous Self-Healing Pipeline (src/state-machine.ts)What it is: A long-running state machine (PLANNING $\rightarrow$ EXECUTING $\rightarrow$ MUTATING $\rightarrow$ VERIFYING).How to leverage it: You can feed this tool a complex, multi-step engineering task (e.g., "Scrape this data, build a localized API endpoint, write unit tests, and deploy"). If the script hits an error at step 3, it doesn't crash. It intercepts the error footprint, rewrites its own execution flags or code blocks, and completes the loop without you lifting a finger.